  "title": "Moonlight Mile",
  "description": "American Air Force pilot Jack F Woodbridge and his Japanese best friend Gorou Saruwatari have finally reached Mount Everest, the final peak on their quest to explore the highest points on Earth. However, unsatisfied, they decide to take on a new challenge: reaching the moon. The world's governments also seek to reach the moon to mine helium-3 as a solution to the energy crisis. The next step for mankind starts here, and Jack and Gorou are going to do everything they can to be the ones making that step. The Moonlight Mile has officially begun.",
